<HEADLINE> Tehran Stock Exchange Index Up </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
TEHRAN, October 3 (Xinhua) -- The general price index at Tehran
Stock Exchange closed at 1767.86 Sunday, up 1.73 points from
Saturday's finish.
</P>
