Sino-Russian diplomatic ties.
</P>
<P>
Nearly 70 participants from both countries had an in-depth
exchange of views on Sino-Russian ties, and they agreed that there
exists a solid social, historical and cultural foundation and
broad prospects for the further growth of Sino-Russian friendship
and cooperation.
</P>
