ambassador to China Igor Rogachev called on youngsters of the two
countries to carry on the cause of Sino-Russian friendship
initiated by elder generations.
</P>
<P>
Sergei Tikhvinsky, honorary chairman of the Central Council of
the Russia-China Friendship Society, and Titarenko, chairman of
the society's Central Council, also praised Sino-Russian relations
at the seminar. 
