<HEADLINE> Kuwait Stock Exchange Index Down </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
KUWAIT CITY, October 4 (Xinhua) -- Kuwait Stock Exchange index
closed at 1,484.1 points Monday, down 7.0 points from Sunday's
finish.
</P>
<P>
The turnover was 4.94 million Kuwaiti dinars (16.30 million
U.S. dollars) as 23.55 million shares were traded in 589 deals.
</P>
