depicted a flying scissor-kick volley from 10 yards to level the
score 1-1 in the 47th minute after Josef Miso put Alajuela ahead
on a penalty kick in the 35th minute.
</P>
<P>
Necaxa midfielder German Villa was sent off the pitch in the
56th minute.
</P>
