the difference?" said Venus who also won their two nontitle
matches in 1998.
</P>
<P>
In the Grand Slam, Serena was all over Venus at the start of
the match, winning 12 of the first 13 points and holding Venus to
three points in the first five games.
</P>
<P>
But Venus got back in the match as Serena's game deteriorated.
</P>
